body: Yes, it is fixed in Clang 9.0. But, as you can see, we have plenty of users on clang-802.0.42 (me included.)  I think in principle, you should be able to install an older version of Xcode and then use xcode-select to put it into your path as the preferred version. Apple LLVM version 8.1.0 (clang-802.0.42) repros the problem.
